<h2 class="Section1" style="margin: 6pt 0cm 4pt 42.8pt; text-indent: -42.8pt;"><span lang="EN-AU" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: arial;">1.3&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Linked documents pre-fixed with an <span class="SpellE">asterix</span> risk are sample documents, all others are mandatory</span></h2>
<h2 class="Section1" style="margin: 6pt 0cm 4pt 28.8pt; text-indent: -28.8pt;"><strong><span lang="EN-AU" style="font-size: 13pt; font-family: arial;">1.4&nbsp;&nbsp; Key Principles</span></strong></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 2pt 0cm 2pt 59.85pt; text-indent: -17.1pt;"><span lang="EN-AU" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: arial;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp; Customer Focus</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 2pt 0cm 2pt 59.85pt; text-indent: -17.1pt;"><span lang="EN-AU" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: arial;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp; Leadership</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 2pt 0cm 2pt 59.85pt; text-indent: -17.1pt;"><span lang="EN-AU" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: arial;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp; Involvement of People</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 2pt 0cm 2pt 59.85pt; text-indent: -17.1pt;"><span lang="EN-AU" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: arial;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp; Process Approach</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 2pt 0cm 2pt 59.85pt; text-indent: -17.1pt;"><span lang="EN-AU" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: arial;">5.&nbsp;&nbsp; System Approach to Management</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 2pt 0cm 2pt 57pt; text-indent: -14.25pt;"><span lang="EN-AU" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: arial;">6.&nbsp; Continual Improvement</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 2pt 0cm 2pt 57pt; text-indent: -14.25pt;"><span lang="EN-AU" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: arial;">7.&nbsp; Factual Approach to Decision Making</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 2pt 0cm 2pt 57pt; text-indent: -14.25pt;"><span lang="EN-AU" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: arial;">8.&nbsp; Mutually beneficial Supplier Relationships</span></p>
<h2 class="Section1" style="margin: 6pt 0cm 4pt 28.8pt; text-indent: -28.8pt;"><strong><span lang="EN-AU" style="font-size: 13pt; font-family: arial;">1.5&nbsp;&nbsp; Context </span></strong></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
