<h2 class="Section1" style="margin: 6pt 0cm 4pt 28.8pt; text-indent: -28.8pt;"><strong><span lang="EN-AU" style="font-size: 13pt; font-family: arial;">1.6&nbsp;&nbsp; Key Corporate Policies</span></strong></h2>
