<h2 class="Section1" style="margin: 6pt 0cm 4pt 28.8pt; text-indent: -28.8pt;"><strong><span lang="EN-AU" style="font-size: 13pt; font-family: arial;">1.7&nbsp;&nbsp; Distribution of Manual </span></strong></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 2pt 0cm 2pt 62.7pt; text-indent: -19.95pt; text-align: justify;"><span lang="EN-AU" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: arial;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The manual is planned to be available online. (In the interim, CD copies will be issued to all on the distribution list). Hard copies are neither issued nor controlled. Notification of revision shall be forwarded to the Group Project all email Alias.</span></p>
<h2 class="Section1" style="margin: 6pt 0cm 4pt 28.8pt; text-indent: -28.8pt;"><strong><span lang="EN-AU" style="font-size: 13pt; font-family: arial;">1.8&nbsp;&nbsp; Manual Composition and Use </span></strong></h2>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 2pt 0cm 2pt 59.85pt; text-indent: -18.15pt;"><span lang="EN-AU" style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: arial;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp; The Manual comprises procedures for 5 basic sections:</span></p>
